# Welcome to Visakan's GitHub Group
Welcome to [Professor Visakan Kadirkamanathan's](http://www.sheffield.ac.uk/acse/staff/vk) GitHub Group. This site aims to gather people and projects that are part of Visakan's group.

## People
There are several people that participate in this group:
* [Parham Aram](https://github.com/parhamaram)
* [Andrew Hills](http://ahills60.github.io)
* [Geoff Holmes](https://github.com/Geoff-Holmes)
* [Yang Zhang](https://github.com/yzhang58)
